						a progetti che abbiano un impatto positivo sulla societ√†. Mi piacerebbe 
						un giorno guidare un team di sviluppatori e condividere la mia esperienza 
						con altri professionisti del settore.
					</p>
					<p>
						Credo che il successo non sia solo nel codice che scrivo, ma anche 
						nelle relazioni che costruisco e nel valore che porto ai progetti 
						e alle persone con cui lavoro.
					</p>
				</section>
			</article>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.about-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.about-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
		padding: 2rem 0;
		border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
	}

	.about-header h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-dark));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.about-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.about-section {
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.about-section h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
		border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
		padding-left: 1rem;
	}

	.about-section p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	/* Philosophy Grid */
	.philosophy-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.philosophy-item {
		background: white;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.philosophy-item:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.philosophy-item h3 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.philosophy-item p {
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	/* Skills Detailed */
	.skills-detailed {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.skill-category-detailed {
		background: white;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
	}

	.skill-category-detailed h3 {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.skill-category-detailed p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.skill-tags-detailed {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.skill-tag-detailed {
		background: var(--accent);
		color: white;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	/* Interests Grid */
	.interests-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.interest-item {
		background: white;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.interest-item:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
	}

	.interest-item h3 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.interest-item p {
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	/* Responsive */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about-header h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.philosophy-grid,
		.interests-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.about-section h2 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
	}
</style>
